Version 0.4.0
-------------

Backwards incompatible: Separate virtualenvs

Each release now gets its own virtualenv for proper separation between
releases. We recommend using wheels to maintain speedy releases, e.g.
using http://doc.devpi.net/


Version 0.3.1
--------------

Bugfix for the `current` symlink creation


Version 0.3.0
--------------

- Delete stack after completion
- Capture instance images after stack creation
- Capture / delete instance images
- Additional tags from cli
- Fixed: instance size lookup based on name
- CloudFormation stack support
- Supervisor start/stop commands

